name: CHRISTMAS IN MORGUE
description:
If you want to celebrate Christmas in a way you've never seen before, try celebrating it at the morgue.

I sat and looked thoughtfully at this cabinet with meat casings for human souls, on which Death sat and looked sadly at the floor.
The cigarette, the smoke of which I can never feel, smoldered between the fingers of my hand.
In the distance, the bells of Krampus's sleigh could be heard.

Cosy.
